lead_paragraph: Gary Neville's appointment as Valencia coach in December stunned the world of football but his sacking on Wednesday was easier to predict, the only surprise being that it did not come sooner.

headline.print_headline: Analysis-Seven-Nil Barca Drubbing Began Neville's Demise
